<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Hermoupolis Magna</placeName></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἑρμαῖος Αἰ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λ</unclear>ίωι Ἀπολλωνίωι 

    <lb n="2"/>τῶι τιμιωτάτωι χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>καὶ ἐν τούτωι καὶ ἐν τοῖς 

    <lb n="4"/>ἄλλοις πᾶσι, κύριε, τὴν ἁρ-

    <lb n="5"/>μόζουσάν σοι εὔνοιάν μοι 

    <lb n="6"/>καὶ φιλίαν παρέχεις καὶ μι-

    <lb n="7"/>κρὸς μὲν ἐγὼ χάριν σοι εἰδέ-

    <lb n="8"/>ναι, οἱ δὲ θεοὶ σέ ἀμείψονται. 

    <lb n="9"/>τὴν προσφώνησιν, ὡς ἐκέ-

    <lb n="10"/>λευσας καὶ ὑπέδειξας, ἔπεμ-

    <lb n="11"/>ψά σοι καὶ ἦλθον ἄν, κύριε, εἰ 

    <lb n="12"/>μὴ σὺ προλαβὼν καὶ περὶ 

    <lb n="13"/>τοῦ τύπου ἔγραψας, καὶ τῶι 

    <lb n="14"/>θεῶι με ἐχαρίσω, παρ᾽ ὧι τὸ 

    <lb n="15"/>προσκύνημά σου ποιῶ με-

    <lb n="16"/>τὰ τῶν σῶν πάντων. <handShift new="m2"/> ἐρρῶσθαί 

    <lb n="17"/>σε εὔχομαι, κύριέ 

    <lb n="18"/>μου. 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="19"/><note anchored="yes" lang="en" place="not specified">m3 ?</note> Αἰλίωι Ἀπολλωνίωι γυμνασιάρχωι </ab></div></div><div n="meta.19633" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.19633" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="0120" notBefore="0117" precision="low" type="textDate">ca. 117 - 120</date></p></div><div n="meta.19633" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Gehört zum Archiv des Strategen Apollonios. Zur Datierung vgl. Bastianini - Whitehorne, Strategi, S. 17 - 18.</p></div><div n="meta.19633" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Brem.</title><biblScope type="numbers">49</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">19633</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0083</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">49</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0083;;49" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.19633" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.19633" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="low" full="yes" type="ancientFindspot">Hermopolis</placeName></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>